_sText:
Originally this was just a map I made because I was bored. At the time I was still learning how to do rounded corners. This map was put off until I polished it up. Then it was put off again and re-polished. So here it is! This map is a replica of the original 2d Pacman game. I tried to spice it up by adding the red and blue colors. This indicates where you are. Red is Terrorists and Blue is Counter-Terrorists. I also made the sides into teleports that teleport you into the middle. Have fun!

Made by Conch
